{
  "stem": "14060.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, OK, that was nothing tragic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next day, appell first thing in the morning, early morning-- what does that mean?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You get lined up in groups of 10 wide and 20 deep, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Counting, and counting, and counting, the never-ending job-- we stand there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we don't know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "OK, that's done.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then back to the barrack, because we were not working there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then eventually was so-called lunch time, if you like, what the food was being.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How did the food look like?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You lined up again like in an appell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one bowl of some watery, which was called [? durgem ?], you say, some floating bits of vegetable-- if you can call it vegetable, or imitation grass, I don't know what-- was given, a bowl in the hand of the guy who stood on the corner and no spoon, no fork, no.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, you know, one came from a normal existence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you get dropped into the pits, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So how do you drink?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "How do you eat?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You take it to your mouth and you drink.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some are older, some are less old, and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One is small.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One is tall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One wants to drink.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The other one is waiting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Give it to me, there won't be enough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I mean, there was not a great deal of talking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was quite a commotion to get used to the feeding exercise, if you know what I mean.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was one thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other thing was that we-- really on the first day got to know when we had an opportunity to talk to anybody, and it went around like wildfire-- can you see the big fire and flame and smoke?",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's where your relatives are going up now.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
